<div class="prof-header text-center">
  <h1 class="prof-title">Learn more</h1>
</div>

  <div>
      <h5 class="subtitle">Angels</h5>
      <p>Choose <b>5 people you trust the most</b>, <i>WithU</i> will call them for you in an emergency situation. Choose wisely, your angels should be <b>reliable</b> people. Add the angels in your profile. </p>
    </div>

  <div>
    <h5 class="subtitle">Screen 1</h5>
    <p>The ringtone starts playing. Send your location immediately if you feel threatened. Decide if you want to accept the fake call to see some more options. Hit <b>2nd call</b> if you need a <b>different recording</b>. If you turn the call down, you will get to the settings. </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h5 class="subtitle">Screen 2</h5>
    <p>You accepted the fake call. The call track <b>starts in 3 seconds</b>. Either, the voice of the speaker already calms you down, or you want to call your angels. Hit the <b>Call Angels</b> button. <i>WithU</i> will connect you to your angels. As soon as an angel picks up the phone, <i>WithU</i> will stop calling the others. In the meanwhile you <b>still</b> have the opportunity to <b>share your location</b>, to <b>interrupt</b> or to <b>stop</b> the fake call. </p>
  </div>

